<main><div class="animated-bg-container" data-astro-cid-do4sevwe><div class="grid-overlay" data-astro-cid-do4sevwe></div><div class="gradient-orb orb-1" data-astro-cid-do4sevwe></div><div class="gradient-orb orb-2" data-astro-cid-do4sevwe></div><div class="gradient-orb orb-3" data-astro-cid-do4sevwe></div><div class="particles" data-astro-cid-do4sevwe></div></div><div class="floating-elements" data-astro-cid-fgearzst><div class="float-shape shape-1" data-astro-cid-fgearzst></div><div class="float-shape shape-2" data-astro-cid-fgearzst></div><div class="float-shape shape-3" data-astro-cid-fgearzst></div><div class="float-shape shape-4" data-astro-cid-fgearzst></div><div class="float-shape shape-5" data-astro-cid-fgearzst></div></div><div class="shapes-3d-container" data-astro-cid-ef6knh6u><canvas data-astro-cid-ef6knh6u id="shapes-canvas"></canvas><div class="spark-container" data-astro-cid-ef6knh6u></div></div><section class="mx-auto relative px-4 max-w-4xl z-10 pb-10 pt-24 sm:pt-28"><span class="text-sm glitch-text text-primary tracking-[0.6em] uppercase" data-astro-cid-5jggg6be data-text="Mission brief">Mission brief</span><header class="border bg-white border-gray-200 px-6 py-10 rounded-[32px] shadow-xl mt-4"><h1 class="font-semibold leading-tight sm:text-3xl text-4xl text-balance text-slate-900">Itinerant polymath who shows up and solves problems</h1><p class="text-xl mt-4 text-slate-600">Drop in, enlight us, and disseapear</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-4 text-slate-500 text-sm"><span class="items-center inline-flex gap-2"><span class="rounded-full bg-emerald-500 h-2 w-2"></span> Earth and beyond / Remote </span><span>Posted Nov 21, 2025</span> <span>Special Contract / Integration</span> <span>DFS</span></div><div class="flex flex-wrap mt-4 font-semibold gap-3 text-xs tracking-wide uppercase"><span class="rounded-full border px-3 py-1 bg-slate-50 border-slate-200 text-slate-700">special-projects</span><span class="rounded-full border px-3 py-1 bg-slate-50 border-slate-200 text-slate-700">systems</span><span class="rounded-full border px-3 py-1 bg-slate-50 border-slate-200 text-slate-700">operations</span> <span class="rounded-full border px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-100 border-emerald-200 text-emerald-700">Remote-friendly</span></div></header></section><section class="mx-auto relative px-4 max-w-4xl z-10 pb-16"><div class="border bg-white border-gray-200 px-6 py-10 rounded-[32px] shadow-xl"><main class="max-w-none prose"><p>Most of our problem can’t be boxed into one discipline, and resolved with a fixed set of tools. Often, even, they cannot be described with words, symbols, or shapes. This is why we need a someone who just gets it, is ready to <em>think real hard</em> and use unconventional means and strategies that lie beyond our ordinary understanding.</p><p>Here at USI, with deal with the <strong>mystical</strong> daily, an it usually cannot be tamed easily.</p><h3 id="what-you-will-do">What you will do</h3><ul><li>Rapidly assess ambiguous problem spaces and propose concrete experiments, methods and protocols.</li><li>Discuss with all departements, bridge ethics with profit, the future and the past.</li><li>Leave behind clear documentation, failed experiments, weird ideas and ambiguous writtings.</li><li>Maintain 24/7 contac</li></ul><h3 id="you-might-be">You might be</h3><ul><li>A mathematician who’s too crazy for conventional research</li><li>A philosopher expert in formal logic and who uses nixos</li><li>A generalist who collects stamps, patents, and strange experiences in equal measure.</li></ul><p>If your people often describe you are “an overly ambitious autistic weirdo” you might want to reach out.</p></main><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-10"><a class="btn-primary" href="mailto:jobs@unsuspicious.org?subject=Itinerant%20Polymath" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Apply for this role</a> <a class="btn-secondary" href="/contact">Talk with our people ops</a></div></div></section></main>
